                     until idx > 25
              move spaces to tpa-el-deposito(idx)
           end-perform.

           inquire gd-mag, last-row in tot-righe.
           perform varying riga from 2 by 1 
                     until riga > tot-righe                   
              inquire gd-mag(riga, 1), cell-data in col-codice
              inquire gd-mag(riga, 3), cell-data in col-gg
              subtract 1 from riga giving idx        
